# Quality Skill

Use this skill when verifying or improving code quality.

## Conventions

- Run `composer lint` for formatting and refactors
- Run `composer test` for the full validation flow
- Run `composer test:types` to validate static analysis
- Prefer fixing root causes instead of silencing tools

## Preferred Order

1. Fix syntax and type issues first
2. Fix static analysis issues
3. Fix formatting issues
4. Re-run the smallest relevant command, then the full suite
